<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Obaveštenje o kreiranoj narudžbi</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Vaša narudžbina je kreirana</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hvala što kupujete kod nas. Vaša narudžbina je primljena i biće poslata u najkraćem mogućem roku.</p>

            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Proizvod</th>
                        <th>Opis</th>
                        <th>Količina</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    @foreach (var item in Model.Order.Items)
                    {
                        <tr>
                            <td>@item.Item.Name</td>
                            <td>@item.Item.Description</td>
                            <td>@item.Quantity</td>
                        </tr>
                    }
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <p style="text-align:right; margin-top: 20px;">Ukupna cena: @Model.Order.TotalPrice RSD</p>

            <p>Srdačno,</p>
            <p>@Model.StoreName</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
